
ftrace = Function Tracer

? ftrace uses the → Linux/filesystem/filesystems#debugfs filesystem to hold the control
files as well as the files to display output.

{ Common uses

  Event tracing

}

{ Prerequisites

  → Linux/kernel/CONFIG/DYNAMIC_FTRACE,
  → Linux/kernel/CONFIG/TRACE_IRQFLAGS_SUPPORT

}

